{
  "sections": {
    "image-banner": {
      "type": "image-banner",
      "blocks": {
        "heading-group": {
          "type": "heading-group",
          "settings": {
            "page_title": true
          },
          "blocks": {
            "heading": {
              "type": "_heading",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "FAQ",
                "heading_size": "h1"
              }
            }
          },
          "block_order": [
            "heading"
          ]
        },
        "text": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>We've gathered answers to the most frequently asked questions to make your shopping experience easier and more enjoyable. </p><p>If you still have any questions or need further assistance, don't hesitate to <a href=\"#\" title=\"Contact\">reach out</a> to our support team. We're here to help and ensure you have the best experience with our products!</p>",
            "font_style": "body"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading-group",
        "text"
      ],
      "settings": {
        "height": "small",
        "mobile_height": "medium",
        "stack": "none",
        "spacing": "0px",
        "media_content_padding": "default",
        "container_type": "full",
        "container_width": "xs",
        "horizontal_alignment": "left",
        "vertical_alignment": "middle",
        "enable_banner_click": false,
        "enable_overlay": false,
        "overlay": "linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(255, 255, 255, 0) 100%)",
        "color_scheme": "scheme-4",
        "enable_color_scheme_transition": false,
        "color_scheme_transition": "",
        "padding_top": "0px",
        "padding_bottom": "0px",
        "show_top_border": false,
        "show_bottom_border": false
      }
    },
    "main": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "heading-group": {
          "type": "heading-group",
          "settings": {
            "page_title": false
          },
          "blocks": {
            "heading": {
              "type": "_heading",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Ordering & Returns",
                "heading_size": "h4"
              }
            }
          },
          "block_order": [
            "heading"
          ]
        },
        "collapsible": {
          "type": "collapsible",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Where does Primavera ship?",
            "font_style": "caption"
          },
          "blocks": {
            "text": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>We currently ship worldwide. Shipping rates and delivery times vary depending on your location. You can view estimated shipping costs at checkout.</p>",
                "font_style": "body"
              }
            }
          },
          "block_order": [
            "text"
          ]
        },
        "collapsible-2": {
          "type": "collapsible",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How long does shipping take?",
            "font_style": "caption"
          },
          "blocks": {
            "text-2": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Orders are typically processed within 1-3 business days. Delivery times depend on your location:</p><ul><li>Domestic (U.S.): 3-7 business days</li><li>Europe: 5-10 business days</li><li>International: 7-14 business days</li></ul><p>Expedited shipping options are available at checkout.</p>",
                "font_style": "body"
              }
            }
          },
          "block_order": [
            "text-2"
          ]
        },
        "collapsible-3": {
          "type": "collapsible",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "What is your return policy?",
            "font_style": "caption"
          },
          "blocks": {
            "text-3": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>We accept returns within 14 days of receiving your order, provided the item is unworn and in its original packaging. Custom or engraved pieces are final sale. To initiate a return, email us at <a href=\"#\" title=\"mailto:returns@primaverajewelry.com\">returns@example.com</a>.</p>",
                "font_style": "body"
              }
            }
          },
          "block_order": [
            "text-3"
          ]
        },
        "collapsible-4": {
          "type": "collapsible",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you offer gift wrapping?",
            "font_style": "caption"
          },
          "blocks": {
            "text-4": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Your pieces will arrive in our 100% recyclable box and reusable cotton pouch. Sending as a gift? Add the finishing touches with our signature gift box, available to add within your cart.</p>",
                "font_style": "body"
              }
            }
          },
          "block_order": [
            "text-4"
          ]
        },
        "collapsible-5": {
          "type": "collapsible",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "How can I track my order?",
            "font_style": "caption"
          },
          "blocks": {
            "text-5": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Once your order ships, you’ll receive a confirmation email with a tracking link. If you haven’t received tracking details within 3 business days, reach out to us at <a href=\"#\" title=\"mailto:support@example.com\">support@example.com</a>.</p>",
                "font_style": "body"
              }
            }
          },
          "block_order": [
            "text-5"
          ]
        },
        "heading-group-2": {
          "type": "heading-group",
          "settings": {
            "page_title": false
          },
          "blocks": {
            "heading-2": {
              "type": "_heading",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Corporate",
                "heading_size": "h4"
              }
            }
          },
          "block_order": [
            "heading-2"
          ]
        },
        "collapsible-6": {
          "type": "collapsible",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Are Primavera products sustainable?",
            "font_style": "caption"
          },
          "blocks": {
            "text-6": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>At Primavera, sustainability is at the heart of everything we do. We are committed to using ethically sourced ingredients, eco-conscious packaging, and responsible production practices to minimize our environmental impact. Our formulations prioritize vegan, cruelty-free, and skin-friendly ingredients, while our packaging is designed with recyclability and reduced waste in mind. We continuously strive to make beauty more sustainable—without compromising on quality or performance.</p>",
                "font_style": "body"
              }
            }
          },
          "block_order": [
            "text-6"
          ]
        },
        "collapsible-7": {
          "type": "collapsible",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "Do you offer wholesale partnerships?",
            "font_style": "caption"
          },
          "blocks": {
            "text-7": {
              "type": "text",
              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>We love partnering with boutiques and retailers. If you’re interested in carrying Primavera, please email us at <a>wholesale@example.com</a>.</p>",
                "font_style": "body"
              }
            }
          },
          "block_order": [
            "text-7"
          ]
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading-group",
        "collapsible",
        "collapsible-2",
        "collapsible-3",
        "collapsible-4",
        "collapsible-5",
        "heading-group-2",
